creator: Evidation Health
descriptionHtml:
Join over three million members getting paid for health actions and who are contributing to cutting edge research!

Our diverse community has contributed to more than 15 prospective studies, which are often published in medical journals like American Heart Journal and Journal of Medical Internet Research.

Achievement was created by industry veterans at Evidation Health. Backed by some of the top investors in the Silicon Valley and driven by a promise to advance health outcomes, Achievement is focused on curing and studying conditions that have yet to be studied by the brightest minds in research and data science.

Achievement is a product of Evidation Health which enables healthcare companies to partner with patients and consumers who are engaged in understanding and improving health outcomes. Evidation’s clients are a wide array of healthcare companies -- innovative digital health products and services, biopharma companies, and academic researchers and institutions.

On the Achievement platform, we pay you to:
-Track steps
-Log food
-Log Meditation sessions
-Answer surveys or opt into a programmatic health challenge

Achievement Studies have researched conditions including:
-Asthma
-Cystic Fibrosis
-Diabetes
-Mental Health
-Migraines
-Rheumatoid Arthritis and more!

”Achievement, which is a division of Evidation Health, helps users integrate a variety of wearable trackers, but in addition to using quantitative data pulled from said trackers, they also posed more qualitative questions of their user base for the purposes of this research. “ --Brit & Co

”Achievement is a service that pays you for tracking your healthy behaviors, such as diet and exercise, water intake and the amount of sleep you get. It connects to apps like FitBit and MyFitnessPal and pays you for the points you accumulate. “
--The New York Times

What’s New:

-Countless bug fixes
-Point Donation to a Health Charity of your choice
-More than $500,000 paid out

Our diverse community has contributed to more than 15 prospective studies, which are often published in medical journals like American Heart Journal and Journal of Medical Internet Research.

Achievement was created by industry veterans at Evidation Health. Backed by some of the top investors in the Silicon Valley and driven by a promise to advance health outcomes, Achievement is focused on curing and studying conditions that have yet to be studied by the brightest minds in research and data science.

Achievement is a product of Evidation Health which enables healthcare companies to partner with patients and consumers who are engaged in understanding and improving health outcomes. Evidation’s clients are a wide array of healthcare companies -- innovative digital health products and services, biopharma companies, and academic researchers and institutions.

On the Achievement platform, we pay you to:
-Track steps
-Log food
-Log Meditation sessions
-Answer surveys or opt into a programmatic health challenge

Achievement Studies have researched conditions including:
-Asthma
-Cystic Fibrosis
-Diabetes
-Mental Health
-Migraines
-Rheumatoid Arthritis and more!

”Achievement, which is a division of Evidation Health, helps users integrate a variety of wearable trackers, but in addition to using quantitative data pulled from said trackers, they also posed more qualitative questions of their user base for the purposes of this research. “ --Brit & Co

”Achievement is a service that pays you for tracking your healthy behaviors, such as diet and exercise, water intake and the amount of sleep you get. It connects to apps like FitBit and MyFitnessPal and pays you for the points you accumulate. “
--The New York Times

What’s New:

-Countless bug fixes
-Point Donation to a Health Charity of your choice
-More than $500,000 paid out
descriptionShort: Achievement-Rewards for Health

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Added the ability to review points statistics and updated the notification preferences.

title: Achievement - Rewards for Health

creator: Evidation Health
descriptionHtml:
Achievement is now Evidation! Our name has changed, but we haven’t. You can still earn points for health actions, participate in groundbreaking research, and receive relevant health articles and personalized insights.

Join over four million members getting paid for health actions. More than $7,000,000 has already been paid out. Evidation is one of the top health apps in the app store.

We pay you cash (via direct deposit, PayPal, gift card, or charity donation) to do healthy things like walking, eating well, and even sleeping! We also provide you with the opportunity to contribute to cutting-edge health research.

"My sister told me about it, and it seemed too good to be true at first. But when she said that she had already received $20, I signed up. It was so easy and a monetary motivation really encouraged me to get up and get moving."- Estella

“I have had back problems for many years. Walking is one of the only ways I keep my back problems under control since the more you move the looser your back becomes and helps blood flow to heal your back. When I have the benefit of making money from keeping myself healthy, I go just a little longer each day." --Kelli C

”...Evidation Health helps users integrate a variety of wearable trackers, but in addition to using quantitative data pulled from said trackers, they also posed more qualitative questions of their user base for the purposes of this research. “ --Brit & Co

We pay you to:
-Track steps
-Log food
-Log meditation sessions
-Log sleep
-Log miles biked
-Answer surveys
-Participate in programmatic health programs
-Contribute to research

CONNECT APPS AND EARN POINTS: Choose from 20+ popular apps (including Apple Health, Fitbit, and Garmin) and start earning points for activities such as walking, meditating, logging meals, and answering questions about yourself.

REDEEM YOUR POINTS FOR CASH OR CHARITIES: Earn $10 for every 10,000 points, redeemable via PayPal, direct deposit, gift card, or by donating your points directly to a charity. Rewards are paid within 3-7 business days.

PARTICIPATE IN CUTTING EDGE RESEARCH: Join health studies and make contributions to our understanding of health. We share insights back with you, and our scientists publish their findings in top medical journals for the benefit of all.

LEARN MORE ABOUT YOUR HEALTH: Join unique health programs designed to help you learn more about your health.

What else can we say? It's literally that easy - we pay you cash to track steps and participate in research, no strings attached! Over 4 million members are already earning money with us, just install and get started!

You may only use Evidation if you are 18 years or older and are a resident of the United States. For more details, visit our Terms of Use at https://www.evidation.com/members/terms
descriptionShort: Evidation-Rewards for Health - Get paid to track your health!

title: Evidation - Rewards for Health

creator: Evidation Health
descriptionHtml:
Earn points for health actions, like walking, sleeping, and more.

How it works
- Complete cards: Answer questions, take surveys & read articles.
- Track health activity: Connect health apps such as Fitbit & Apple Health.

What you get
- Health trends & insights: Make sense of your data—from step count to sleep patterns.
- Points redeemable for cash: Cash out or donate $10 for every 10,000 points.
- Research opportunities: If eligible, receive invites to participate in health programs or research studies.
- Personalized content: Receive health tips, articles & more.

Our data practices
- We’re committed to trust & transparency at all times.
- We do not & will not sell your personal information.
- Your health data is shared only with your consent or at your request.

Ready to become an Evidation Member?

Join almost five million members reaching their goals and getting paid for health actions.

Reach your health goals and securely participate in cutting-edge research with the Evidation app! From receiving relevant articles and personalized insights to earning cash for healthy actions, the app makes it easier than ever to stay motivated.

"My sister told me about it, and it seemed too good to be true at first. But when she said that she had already received $20, I signed up. It was so easy and a monetary motivation really encouraged me to get up and get moving."- Estella

“I have had back problems for many years. Walking is one of the only ways I keep my back problems under control since the more you move the looser your back becomes and helps blood flow to heal your back. ”...Evidation Health helps users integrate a variety of wearable trackers, but in addition to using quantitative data pulled from said trackers, they also posed more qualitative questions of their user base for the purposes of this research. “ --Brit & Co

We pay you to:
- Track steps
- Log food
- Log meditation sessions
- Log sleep
- Log miles biked
- Answer surveys
- Read health related tips and content
- Participate in health programs
- Contribute to research

ELEVATE YOUR HEALTH JOURNEY: From heart health to flu monitoring, join unique programs designed to help you learn more about your health. Whether reading tips for disease prevention or answering questions about your daily habits and health conditions, your participation also earns you points redeemable for cash.

CONNECT APPS AND EARN POINTS: With options to securely connect 20+ popular apps (including Samsung Health, Fitbit and Garmin), start earning points for daily healthy activities such as walking, meditating, logging meals, and answering questions about yourself.

REDEEM YOUR POINTS FOR CASH OR CHARITIES: Earn $10 for every 10,000 points, redeemable via PayPal, direct deposit, gift card, or by donating your points directly to charity.

PARTICIPATE IN CUTTING EDGE RESEARCH: Use the app as one-stop shop to find, match with, and opt in to health studies and contribute to findings published in top medical journals for the benefit of all. In exchange, you’ll receive personalized insights to give you a deeper understanding of your health.

descriptionHtml:
Take control of your health and contribute to groundbreaking medical research— all while earning rewards for everyday activities! Evidation empowers you to track your everyday health activities and efforts, sync with leading health apps and wearables, and participate in cutting-edge health studies that drive scientific discoveries. By sharing your health data securely, you can help shape the future of healthcare while gaining valuable insights into your well-being.

Join a Health Research Community That Makes an Impact

Evidation partners with top universities, medical institutions, and public health organizations to conduct innovative research on chronic conditions, disease prevention, and overall wellness. Your participation supports advancements in areas such as heart health, diabetes, mental wellness, sleep patterns, and more.

Earn Rewards from Everyday Activities

With Evidation, healthy choices pay off. Earn points for activities like walking, sleeping, tracking your heart rate, and answering short health surveys. Whether you’re logging your steps, syncing with a fitness tracker, or reading personalized health articles, you’ll earn rewards that can be redeemed for cash, gift cards, or charitable donations. Evidation makes it easy to stay motivated while making meaningful contributions to health research.

Key Features:
- Track & Sync Health Data: Securely connect with Fitbit, Apple Health, Google Fit, Samsung Health, Oura, and other wearables to function seamlessly with your health tracking.
- Participate in Health Research: Contribute to studies that help improve medical knowledge and public health outcomes.
- Earn Rewards for Health Actions: Get paid for tracking steps, sleep, weight, heart rate, exercise and more.
- Receive Personalized Insights: Gain evidence-based insights tailored to your health and wellness goals.

How It Works
- Track Your Health: Log activities, sync wearables, and monitor trends in sleep, physical activity, and heart health.
- Answer Health Surveys: Provide valuable feedback on lifestyle habits, chronic conditions, and wellness routines.
- Engage in Research: Receive invitations to participate in clinical and observational studies relevant to your health profile.
- Get Rewarded: Earn points redeemable for cash, gift cards, or charitable donations.

Our data practices
- We’re committed to trust & transparency at all times.
- We do not & will not sell your personal information.
- Your health data is shared only with your consent or at your request.

Participate in research opportunities while maintaining full control over your information.

Join Millions Contributing to Health Research

With nearly 5 million members, Evidation is helping to redefine how individuals engage with their health while advancing critical research. From understanding flu trends to improving heart disease prevention strategies, your participation has a real-world impact.
